@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_meftfo(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = (v2 - ((v1 + 0.75 / v2 + 0.13) + v0))
    v1 = wp.exp(wp.cos(wp.abs(v1 + 0.09)))
    tmp = (((v2 + 0.68 + v1 + 0.85) + 0.14) / ((v0 + 0.45 / v2 + 0.81) - wp.cos(tmp + 0.80)))
    data[tid] = v0
